# Preventive 404s for internal/private content patterns that must never be served.
# Cloudflare Pages honors this file at the site root. Missing files return 404 by
# default; these rules extend that guarantee to specific filenames even if a file
# were ever accidentally committed under one of these paths.
/guide-build-brief.html          /  404
/guide/guide-build-brief.html    /  404
/GUIDE-BUILD-BRIEF*              /  404
/*methodology*                   /  404
/*METHODOLOGY*                   /  404
/*build-brief*                   /  404
/*BUILD-BRIEF*                   /  404
/*.internal.*                    /  404
